op/handle-type-mismatch

  × op `resize` argument `target`: handle `@bad` is a tab, expected a pane
   ╭─[scene.kdl:1:13]
 1 │ scene "x" { bad }
   ·             ─┬─
   ·              ╰── wrong handle type here
   ╰────
  help: Check R7's op vocabulary for the required handle type on this argument. Pane-only ops (`resize`, `pin`, `unpin`, `move`) reject tab handles; tab-only ops (`rename`, `new_tab`) reject pane
        handles.
